title: Windows Vista, every version, seperate iso. files+activator
description: Here it is. every version of windows vista plus an activator. they did not need the activator on my hp, but use it to be safe. to use go to nero, select Burning rom, then dvd rom boot and burn to a dvd. save the activator to a cd like any other exe. file. they are seperate iso files so have fun. ultimate has an error pop up at first start up, just close the popup, ultimate worked a charm for me.
